{
  "title": "Tender Braised Chinese Napa Cabbage Bao",
  "description": "A savory and light Chinese dish featuring braised napa cabbage in a sweet and sour brine, served in a fluffy bao bun, perfect for a weeknight dinner",
  "cuisine": "Chinese",
